  "description": "Find your nearest weighbridge if you need to weigh your van, lorry, trailer, tractor or other vehicle",
  "details": {
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introduction": "<p>Find your nearest weighbridge if you need to weigh your van, lorry, trailer, tractor or other vehicle.</p>\n",
    "lgil_code": 8,
    "lgsl_code": 1742,
    "more_information": "<p>Most weighbridges are operated by private businesses.</p>\n\n<p>You should contact the weighbridge operator before going to check:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>how much it costs to use</li>\n  <li>how to get there</li>\n  <li>their operating hours</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You should also tell the operator if you have a very large vehicle, to make sure it will fit on the weighbridge.</p>\n",
    "need_to_know": "\n",
    "service_tiers": [
      "county",
      "unitary"
    ]
  },
